latestPosts.caption:
Fully obsessed with @yslbeauty! These lip stains wear super light, stay on for hours, and are crazy hydrating!

The first shade is the Vinyl Cream in Nude Champion - it has a glossy vibe to it, but it stayyyys on! 

The second one is the Vinyl Blur in Red Invitation - I loved this too much! I don’t like wearing a heavy red. So this just works for me. 

Also special shoutout to @yslbeauty’s mascara. IT’S THE BEST! UNMATCHED!
